    <sys:String x:Key="LOC_SHS_ForceUpdateTooltip">If enabled, always recreates shortcuts from scratch when they are updated.</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="LOC_SHS_UpdateOnStartUpTooltip">If enabled, updates shortcuts to games on startup.</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="LOC_SHS_ExcludeHiddenTooltip">If enabled, hidden games are ingored when creating shortcuts and shortcuts of hidden games are removed on update.</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="LOC_SHS_SeparateFoldersTooltip">If enabled, shortcuts will be placed into a subfolder inside the Shortcut Path named after their Source.</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="LOC_SHS_FadeEdgesTooltip">If enabled, the bottom of the tile background images are faded out to improve readability of the title, if the title is visible.</sys:String>
